    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been treated with lots of love? This beauty is in great shape and runs like a dream. It\u2019s got a few miles of character, but it\u2019s super clean and ready for its next adventure with you! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll feel the difference the moment you get behind the wheel. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014I'd love to find it a great new home!",
